title: BIG FACTS feat. JEEZY
itunes:title: BIG FACTS feat. JEEZY
description:
Jeezy sits down with the BIG FACTS team at ATL’s Trap Music Museum ahead of the release of his SNOFALL mixtape.

The conversation covers the project, the VERZUZ battle with Gucci Mane, his personal progression and evolution, his former business partner Kink B and more!

| Visit: www.bigfactspod.com

| For Merch: bigfactsmerch.myshopify.com

| Follow: @BigFactsPod
